short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save and quickly view your regular commuting routes in Sweden

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Before you can view your trips you need to select two stops in the options of this extension. You will be guided to do this if you have not when you open the extensions for the first time.

The following trips between the saved stops will be viewable when the extension is opened.
